      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## GatewayZ — Error Log Analysis\nLoki-powered view of every ERROR and CRITICAL log line emitted by the backend.\n\n| Section | What it shows |\n|---------|---------------|\n| Error Rate | Volume of ERROR/CRITICAL events per minute — this metric spikes before 5xx rates rise in Prometheus |\n| Log Stream | Live tail of error logs with full message body — includes provider timeouts, Redis failures, and auth rejections |\n| Top Patterns | Most frequent error messages grouped by content — distinguishes a flood of identical errors from diverse, independent failures |",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.5.2",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
